The `buildCanonicalName()` method in `ReferenceType.java` was generating canonical names like `java.util.concurrent.atomic.AtomicReference<java.lang.Long` instead of `java.util.concurrent.atomic.AtomicReference<java.lang.Long>` - missing the closing `>` bracket.

